TY  - JOUR
TI  - Existence of Competitive Equilibria in Markets with a Continuum of Traders
AU  - Aumann, Robert J.
AB  - [An appropriate model for a market with many individually insignificant traders is one with a continuum of traders. Here it is proved that competitive equilibria exist in such markets, even though individual preferences may not be convex. Such a result is not true for markets with finitely many traders.]
