TY  - JOUR
TI  - Rational Distributed Lag Functions
AU  - Jorgenson, Dale W.
AB  - [The purpose of this paper is to introduce a class of distributed lag functions having the properties that an arbitrary distributed lag function may be approximated to any desired degree of accuracy by a member of this class and that the number of parameters required for a satisfactory approximation is less than that required for an equally good approximation by a finite distributed lag function.]
